 "prompt": "A sleek, obsidian black, palm-sized neuro-harmonizer device with a subtle purple glowing core, A stark, desaturated urban high-rise office at peak stress hour, chaotic and claustrophobic, Sophisticated East Asian woman in her late 30s, sharp, intelligent, elegant, wearing minimalist attire, MS of the woman looking stressed, surrounded by papers and monitors, other stressed employees blurred in the background, Low-Key lighting, ARRI Alexa, Handheld to Steadycam, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
